About the Map

This map compiles articles about current candidates in the 2025 Federal Election. Click on a riding, or enter the name of your riding to get started.

Don't know your riding? Follow this link to find out.

We've compiled a list of the candidates from each major party (sourced from each party's website) and included articles we have found mentioning these candidates. Are we missing a candidate? Contact us here.

The Federal Electoral District Riding map was sourced directly from the Government of Canada Open Government Website.
